Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.31,0:06:58.65,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いつだって　いっぱいの夢だけを
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.94,0:07:03.99,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けてあげるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.59,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}眺めていた星空は
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.92,0:07:27.05,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}思ったよりも　大きかったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.05,0:07:32.31,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}叫んでみても　まだ届かない
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.31,0:07:36.89,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世界は広く眩しい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.23,0:07:42.57,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}叶えてみたい　願いごと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.57,0:07:47.86,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}たくさん胸叩いてるけど
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.91,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}手始めにさ　見てみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.91,0:07:56.33,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君の笑顔の　とびきりを
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.37,0:08:03.96,opjp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an1}まっすぐに　見つめててほしいよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.96,opjp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an3}ずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.05,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}幸せあげたいから
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.05,0:08:14.47,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an1}いつだって　いっぱいの夢だけを
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.47,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an3}君に
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.52,0:08:19.48,opjp,,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}届けよう　Longing for the happiness!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.31,0:06:58.65,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不論何時  都懷揣無數的夢想
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.94,0:07:03.99,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}並將其贈送於你
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.59,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}仰望所見的星空
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.92,0:07:27.05,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}比想像中更加廣闊
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.05,0:07:32.31,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即便高聲呼喊  仍卻無法傳達
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.31,0:07:36.89,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}世界真是遼闊而耀眼
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.23,0:07:42.57,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}有好多期待實現的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.57,0:07:47.86,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不斷敲打著我的心扉
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.91,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}想自始至終看到
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.91,0:07:56.33,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}你那格外燦爛的笑容
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.37,0:08:03.96,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an9}想要你坦率地注視著我
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.96,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an7}直至永遠
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.05,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我想要為你帶來幸福
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.05,0:08:14.47,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an9}不論何時  都懷揣無數的夢想
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.47,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3\an7}贈送於你
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.52,0:08:19.48,opcn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}傳送到吧  Longing for the happiness!
